{"tid":498810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚週年食乜好","createTime":"2017-12-14T06:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T01:30:39.000Z","uid":45309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9c5536fa248818414e388d49f213fef248147c","tid":498810,"uid":45309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"同老婆結婚週年, 有無推介?<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過跑馬地AMIGO, 暫時覺得OK, 有花有禮物有live band 有蛋榚<br />\n但有人話d 野食質素唔值咁貴<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以推介其他? budget無上限"},{"pid":"486d268e5bbdb1796efe1d8742f4b8f5d28e9773","tid":498810,"uid":43924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"你上連登問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac617ae4d6c0eb780c454644cf9061f320be32e","tid":498810,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"去麥記開party <br />\n一定好驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c8dc00a3106d98ed10bf1038ebe810a9e18f48","tid":498810,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"如果要食景<br />\nintercon 個堆餐廳都ok, 另外海港城開左間新法日餐廳都有海景 而野食又唔錯<br />\n<br />\n如果講野食<br />\n可以揀amber, grand hyatt steak house, tate 等等<br />\n<br />\namigo啲食物真係中挺only"},{"pid":"fe2faac92416e36db1ca8016cc245ad97f32da55","tid":498810,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果要食景<br />\nintercon 個堆餐廳都ok, 另外海港城開左間新法日餐廳都有海景 而野食又唔錯<br />\n<br />\n如果講野食<br />\n可以揀amber, grand hyatt steak house, tate 等等<br />\n<br />\namigo啲食物真係中挺only</blockquote><br />\n怡東Tott 點睇？"},{"pid":"68382b2c1e9da65b7da1b2295a6bd24fcae128aa","tid":498810,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去麥記開party <br />\n一定好驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdc75158c77c6c2b75cb5a5f41d139d2ec97b4e","tid":498810,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果要食景<br />\nintercon 個堆餐廳都ok, 另外海港城開左間新法日餐廳都有海景 而野食又唔錯<br />\n<br />\n如果講野食<br />\n可以揀amber, grand hyatt steak house, tate 等等<br />\n<br />\namigo啲食物真係中挺only</blockquote><br />\n怡東Tott 點睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未食過 睇相一般"},{"pid":"473e6354253a534de78a2b16d392398145aad12b","tid":498810,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"一個食西一個食腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fdbbb96805397469ade7182d849dc36c7f7c10","tid":498810,"uid":45309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果要食景<br />\nintercon 個堆餐廳都ok, 另外海港城開左間新法日餐廳都有海景 而野食又唔錯<br />\n<br />\n如果講野食<br />\n可以揀amber, grand hyatt steak house, tate 等等<br />\n<br />\namigo啲食物真係中挺only</blockquote><br />\n睇左amber，唔多岩食<br />\n<br />\ngrand hyatt 睇落ok<br />\n<br />\n有無d 同amigo 一樣特別少少手有小禮物？"},{"pid":"f1034ef80ceb78cb14f19a322ce055142d2dca0a","tid":498810,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果要食景<br />\nintercon 個堆餐廳都ok, 另外海港城開左間新法日餐廳都有海景 而野食又唔錯<br />\n<br />\n如果講野食<br />\n可以揀amber, grand hyatt steak house, tate 等等<br />\n<br />\namigo啲食物真係中挺only</blockquote><br />\n睇左amber，唔多岩食<br />\n<br />\ngrand hyatt 睇落ok<br />\n<br />\n有無d 同amigo 一樣特別少少手有小禮物？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你堅持舊派大排場氣氛 <br />\n要個d玫瑰呀簿仔 咁揀返amigo算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多一家大細普通食飯都係amigo 所以我又唔覺amigo有咩特別 同埋我比較睇重食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea3be244412a19cf16b562bb0028bd3703edfe2","tid":498810,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:52:46.000Z","msg":"Petrus 味道好 環境好 <br />\n <br />\nAmigo 質素差左 但環境無變 都浪漫<br />\n<br />\n結婚週年 就算間餐廳冇小禮物 你自己預備一份都得嘅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38aa5eb3a19cccd1f31733495f2cade33631aa3","tid":498810,"uid":3579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"我一週年時喺屋企煎扒同開蠔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完蠔就梗係即刻開波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}